    "description": "This Sign-In Form component is a sleek and minimal authentication interface built with ShadCN UI and Lucide icons, designed to fit seamlessly into both light and dark themes. It combines traditional email/password login with social login options like Google, Apple, and GitHub, displayed using clean, self-hosted icons for consistent rendering across environments. The layout avoids clutter, presenting inputs and actions in a balanced way that emphasizes usability.",
